				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ai-v%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C3%B4n/poem-LP68Aop4_S5Jf74CeC8Mjg">Ai vương tôn - 哀王孫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Loan-Loan/Bi-gi%C3%A0-t%E1%BB%A9-ph%C3%A1ch-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-nh%E1%BB%8B-ph%C3%A1ch/poem-Q4sNTc7vAM9ehrn_IIUbAA">Bi già tứ phách - đệ nhị phách - 悲笳四拍－第二拍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Loan-Loan/author-37QNViodCzbNj28eS0C3jA">Triệu Loan Loan</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Chu-trung-kh%E1%BB%95-nhi%E1%BB%87t-khi%E1%BB%83n-ho%C3%A0i-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-tr%C3%ACnh-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-trung-th%E1%BB%ABa-th%C3%B4ng-gi%E1%BA%A3n-%C4%91%C3%A0i-t%E1%BB%89nh-ch%C6%B0-c%C3%B4ng/poem-QLAaBguKMeDM4PyyaN2VOg">Chu trung khổ nhiệt khiển hoài, phụng trình Dương trung thừa thông giản đài tỉnh chư công - 舟中苦熱遣懷奉呈陽中丞通簡臺省諸公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%E1%BB%99t/%C4%90%E1%BA%B1ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-c%C3%A1c-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-FT3LNnXR5KVN9HD70_hBOw">Đằng Vương các tự - 滕王閣序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%E1%BB%99t/author-_ZqxSvkbsUwNbnMEINI85Q">Vương Bột</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/%C4%90%E1%BB%95ng-H%E1%BB%93-b%C3%BAt-ph%C3%BA/poem-zjv_6tPCykW3dsLfeEVU1g">Đổng Hồ bút phú - 董狐筆賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/H%C3%A0n-bi/poem-aUyDGdFMte6NkDc2IR5eWA">Hàn bi - 韓碑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/Ma-nhai-k%E1%BB%B7-c%C3%B4ng-bi-v%C4%83n/poem-vLWB5X1xeK9ldgaa5hKuGQ">Ma nhai kỷ công bi văn - 磨崖紀功文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-n8TXz8ZnEQ2g7U6IvK74Vw">Nguyễn Trung Ngạn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Hoa-cung/poem-jxxf2eQjKfNe-GYWlVp-gg">Ngọc Hoa cung - 玉華宮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-th%E1%BA%ADp-b%C3%A1t-Ph%E1%BA%A7n/poem-iNvJ6tBHRWQrfqVP1mxB_Q">Tặng Trịnh thập bát Phần - 贈鄭十八賁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90i%E1%BB%81n-V%C4%83n/V%C3%A3n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-ngo%E1%BA%A1-Ph%E1%BA%ADt-t%E1%BB%B1-t%C3%BAc/poem-3rNIoAoDqOHx74Vowx1t6w">Vãn đầu ngoạ Phật tự túc - 晚投卧佛寺宿</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90i%E1%BB%81n-V%C4%83n/author-YRPIo4Mo7rLUlekzN0t78w">Điền Văn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
